                                                                  </svg>
                                                               </button>
                                                               <div class="accordion-body" aria-hidden="true" id="content-who-are-the-experts-behind-the-scenes" style="display:none;">
                                                                  <p>Our team of investing experts make decisions about our<span>&nbsp;</span><a data-track-event="ElementClicked" data-track-module="OurExpertsSection" data-track-name="PortfolioStrategies" href="investments-1.html" data-interaction-listener-registered="true" rel="noopener">portfolio strategies</a><span>&nbsp;</span>and fund selection with the help of an external committee of economists, PhDs, and industry experts.</p>
                                                                  <p>More than just a portfolio management team, our experts work to develop improvements to our<span>&nbsp;</span><a data-track-event="ElementClicked" data-track-module="OurExpertsSection" data-track-name="TaxSmartTechnology" href="tax-efficient-investing-1.html" data-interaction-listener-registered="true" rel="noopener">Tax Smart technology</a>, our cash analysis tools, and other advanced strategies.</p>
